\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces Split-model pipeline with BIE, DP, and SMPC intervention points. The hospital trust boundary contains the raw X-ray, the encoder, and the embedding; the cloud sees only privatized values and the head. BIE perturbs the input image, DP adds Laplace noise to the 128-d embedding, and SMPC distributes additive shares of the embedding across two non-colluding servers that reconstruct it inside the cloud before classification. The diagram depicts the general pipeline with all three mechanisms enabled; individual experimental configurations may activate any subset (Section~\ref {sec:results}, Table~\ref {tab:results}).}}{5}{}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:pipeline}{{3}{5}{}{figure.3}{}}
